data.description: Charming cottage in city of Franklin ready for it's new owners! Walking in, you'll enjoy the original hardwood floors and character this precious home has to offer. Kitchen offers bead board walls, stainless appliances, and generous counter space. Off the kitchen, there is a spacious mudroom and huge bonus room that can be used as a second living room, home office, playroom, game room, or potentially a 4th bedroom. Stepping into the backyard, you'll find a fully fenced in backyard, chicken coop, detached garage with workshop for all your hobbies and crafts! Roof is 6 years old, and in last four years sellers have updated the electrical panel, updated necessary plumbing, replaced floors (and subfloors) in some areas and replaced the hot water heater. Call for your showing today!
